@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Transition Lead" as TL
actor "Privacy Officer" as PO
actor "Legal Representative" as LR
actor "Cron Scheduler" as Timer <<External System>>

rectangle "AMS Intake Platform" {
  usecase "Register stakeholder details" as UC1
  usecase "Upload authorization evidence" as UC2
  usecase "Evaluate intake readiness" as UC3
  usecase "Generate discovery deficit report" as UC4
  usecase "Audit sensitive evidence access" as UC5
  usecase "Purge abandoned intake sessions" as UC6
}

TL --> UC1
TL --> UC2
TL --> UC3

' Evaluate readiness optionally extends to generating a deficit report if data is missing
UC4 .> UC3 : <<extend>> (if missing data)

PO --> UC5
LR --> UC2 : (Validates)
Timer --> UC6

' Note about Variant 9 Privacy Rule
note right of UC1 : Strictly limited to\nCorporate Email and Role (GDPR)
note right of UC6 : Hard-delete after\n30 days of inactivity

@enduml
